## Crear proy django
django-admin startproject institucion
cd institucion
python manage.py startapp escuela

## modificar models, admin y settings
https://gist.github.com/reroes/a00e9bfc88b45af17f0e8788322638d3

python manage.py makemigrations escuela
python manage.py migrate
python manage.py createsuperuser (admin admin)
python manage.py runserver   http://127.0.0.1:8000/admin/  (admin admin)

